===========================================
HAWAII MAKER STUDIO - SCHEMA DOCUMENTATION
===========================================

This theme now includes comprehensive schema markup settings that can be managed through:
Shopify Admin → Online Store → Themes → Customize → Theme Settings → "Schema & SEO Settings"

IMPLEMENTED SCHEMAS:
===================

1. LOCAL BUSINESS SCHEMA (schema-local-business.liquid)
   - Helps with local SEO and Google My Business integration
   - Configurable business info, address, hours, social media
   - Settings: enable_local_business_schema, business_name, business_type, etc.

2. BREADCRUMB SCHEMA (schema-breadcrumbs.liquid)  
   - Shows navigation paths in Google search results
   - Automatically generates breadcrumbs for all page types
   - Settings: enable_breadcrumb_schema

3. WEBSITE SCHEMA (schema-website.liquid)
   - Adds search box to your brand's Google results
   - Enables site search functionality in SERPs
   - Settings: enable_website_schema

4. ENHANCED PRODUCT SCHEMA (schema-enhanced-product.liquid)
   - Extends Shopify's default product schema
   - Includes detailed review/rating data
   - Settings: enable_review_schema, default_rating, default_review_count

5. FAQ SCHEMA (schema-faq.liquid)
   - Makes FAQs appear directly in search results
   - Supports product-specific FAQs via metafields
   - Includes common product FAQs (shipping, returns, warranty)
   - Settings: enable_faq_schema, enable_product_faq_schema

USAGE EXAMPLES:
==============

In templates:
{% render 'schema-local-business' %}
{% render 'schema-breadcrumbs' %}
{% render 'schema-website' %}
{% render 'schema-enhanced-product', product: product %}
{% render 'schema-faq', product: product %}

Custom FAQ usage:
{% assign custom_faqs = '[{"question": "How to use?", "answer": "Follow the guide"}]' | parse_json %}
{% render 'schema-faq', faqs: custom_faqs %}

METAFIELD SETUP FOR PRODUCT FAQS:
=================================

To use custom product FAQs, set up these metafields:
- Namespace: custom
- Key: faq_questions
- Type: Single line text
- Value: Question 1||Question 2||Question 3

- Namespace: custom  
- Key: faq_answers
- Type: Multi-line text
- Value: Answer 1||Answer 2||Answer 3

TESTING YOUR SCHEMA:
===================

1. Enable "Debug Mode" in Schema & SEO Settings
2. Check browser console for schema debug info
3. Use Google's Rich Results Test: https://search.google.com/test/rich-results
4. Use Schema Markup Validator: https://validator.schema.org/

